Subject: net/af_iucv: fix null pointer dereference on shutdown
Git-commit: 4031eeafa71eaf22ae40a15606a134ae86345daf
Patch-mainline: v5.10-rc4
References: bsc#1179567 LTC#190111

syzbot reported the following KASAN finding:

